creator: jux
descriptionHtml:
Dating is hard, especially if tinder and co. don't work for you. You might have to approach hundreds, before finding a person that you really want to go on a date with AND that really wants to go on a date with you. And out in the field, things can get very messy: You might only get rejections one day and return home disheartened. While on another day you might get so many numbers that you forget half of their names!

The NoGame app is here to support you on both ends: It helps you organize potential dates and store information about them, so you never loose track of the opportunities you want to pursue. And if you are still working on your cold approach, the app supports you with this too: It makes it easy to collect and analyze data on every approach, so you can make sense of the outcome, consolidate your learnings, and systematically overcome your sticking points.

In order to get better at something, you have to start measuring it! Why would it be different with dating? Download the app for free and see where it takes you.
descriptionShort: Take your game to the next level

appDetails.recentChangesHtml: This is the very first public release. It provides the basic functionality for tracking and analyzing the user's approaches.

title: NoGame

creator: jux
descriptionHtml:
Cold approach pickup is hard - but online dating is for losers. Let this app help you stay motivated and focused on your way to mastery. Because extraordinary results require extraordinary measures:
• Quantify your progress by keeping track of all your approach and dating outcomes
• Write field reports and collect your learnings so you never make the same mistake twice.
• Manage your leads and build your dating funnel.
• Get statistical insights on your dating outcomes and find the behavior patterns that hold you back.

Coming soon:
• Share field reports with the community and get support from a global network of coaches.a
• Find wing men and wing groups near you for sarging & meetups.

appDetails.recentChangesHtml:
• Lay count calculated correctly
• Performance optimization
• Automatic pursuit status changes improved

title: NoGame

creator: jux
descriptionHtml:
Meeting new people is hard - especially if you’re looking for a date! This app helps you build the confidence to walk up to attractive strangers and start great conversations in real life. Stop waiting for the perfect match on tinder. Take destiny into your hands and learn to meet awesome people anywhere.

Current features:

• Keep track of your dates and interactions
• Measure and analyse your progress
• Manage your leads and build a dating funnel
• Write reflections and capture your learnings
• Share your activity and experiences with a supportive community

Coming soon:

• Start a session and invite other users to go out together

appDetails.recentChangesHtml:
• Complete design revamp
• Gender neutral wording
• Enhanced stability & bugfixes
